internalEmail()

Description
    internalEmail(string $email)
	Checks whether $engineVars['internalEmails'] contains $email.

Parameters
    email
		String variable containing an e-mail message.
		
Return Values
    Returns TRUE upon success.  FALSE otherwise.
	
Examples
	<?php
		...
		if(filter_var($email, FILTER_VALIDATE_EMAIL)) {
			if($internal) {
				if (internalEmail($email)) {
					return(TRUE);
				}
				return(FALSE);
			}
			return(TRUE);
		}
		...
	?>

See Also
	mailSender::sendEmailBulk()